Description: Package calculates landscape and shape metrics for categorical landscape patterns in 
    a tidy workflow. 'vectormetrics' reimplements the most common landscapemetrics from
    'FRAGSTATS' (<https://www.fragstats.org/>) and 'landscapemetrics' (<https://r-spatialecology.github.io/landscapemetrics/>) and 
    adds many new metrics relating to shape of polygons, based on literature. This package supports Simple Feature objects 
    as input arguments. It further provides utility functions to break multipolygon patches or calculate main axes of the shape.
